### List devops workflows
POST http://mcp-devops:8425/invoke
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "tool": "list_workflows",
  "arguments": {}
}

### Run idc1 stack status
POST http://mcp-devops:8425/invoke
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "tool": "run_workflow",
  "arguments": {
    "workflow_id": "idc1-stack-status"
  }
}

### Run idc1 health sweep
POST http://mcp-devops:8425/invoke
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "tool": "run_workflow",
  "arguments": {
    "workflow_id": "idc1-health-sweep"
  }
}
